.el .ds Aq '
.TH ox-serve 1  "ox-serve " 
.SH NAME
ox\-serve \- Start the MCP server for AI agent integration
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBox\-serve\fR [\fB\-\-mcp\fR] [\fB\-\-workdir\fR] [\fB\-\-log\-level\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Start the MCP server for AI agent integration
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-mcp\fR
Start the MCP (Model Context Protocol) server over stdio
.TP
\fB\-\-workdir\fR \fI<WORKDIR>\fR
Working directory for Oxymakefile resolution
.TP
\fB\-\-log\-level\fR \fI<LOG_LEVEL>\fR [default: info]
Log level for stderr diagnostics
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
